  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8361980">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8361980/" class="title-link">醒掌天下权，醉卧美人膝</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8361980"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/150464440/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u150464440-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/150464440/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">张林</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-02-15"
      class="main-meta">2017-02-15 18:06:27</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8361980_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  广度有余，深度不足，对世界上所发生的问题和矛盾有了一些总体的概念，但对问题的延伸却有些泛泛而谈。 很喜欢金一南，在军事栏目中经常见到他，往往以一种幽默诙谐的语言和态度，直指国际关系的本质。看他的书也一样，仿佛他就在你面前，如同一个朋友和讨论者，轻描淡写，却又...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8361980_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8361980_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










